{"word":"φλέψ","slug":"φλέψ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φλέψ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φλέω'><el>φλέω</el></a>?\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a vein</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>φλέβα σχάζειν</el> to open <i>a vein</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a vein</i> of metal, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}